This a sample classification project based on Learning Based Java (LBJava). 
Author: Vivek Srikumar
Updated: Stephen Mayhew, Daniel Khashabi 


#### HOW TO RUN #### 

LINUX
====== 
run: 
./scripts/compileLBJ lbj/SpamClassifier.lbj

if you want to run training again, remove the edu directory under lbjsrc.

WINDOWS
====== 
.\scripts\compileLBJ.bat lbj\SpamClassifier.lbj


#### EXTERNAL LINKS 
The homepage of LBJ:  http://cogcomp.cs.illinois.edu/page/software_view/LBJ 
If you have any questions visit http://cogcomp.cs.illinois.edu/ 